# API Configuration Template

This template provides a sample API configuration block.

## Configuration Parameters

```
api_token = "sk-ant-51MfahoumnZZpNv38raLfCSnQABpNkQzA00ERTAS"
```

## Usage

Replace the `api_token` value with your actual API token when using this configuration in your application.
